wanted to apologize.

01:15:42.166 --> 01:15:43.333
So, go ahead.

01:15:44.208 --> 01:15:46.208
Oh, I can see this
is gonna be fun.

01:15:48.333 --> 01:15:49.333
All right,

01:15:50.208 --> 01:15:51.208
when we were together,

01:15:53.041 --> 01:15:54.375
