01:15:57.333 --> 01:15:58.999
and then you and I,

01:16:01.374 --> 01:16:03.239
and it felt right,

01:16:03.625 --> 01:16:05.958
and I know somehow
it did for you, too.

01:16:07.398 --> 01:16:09.698
