know why we're at lunch.

01:23:12.944 --> 01:23:15.291
Oh, and also Ronnie
told me this morning

01:23:15.302 --> 01:23:16.532
about your little arrangement,

01:23:16.542 --> 01:23:18.542
and I don't approve.

01:23:18.625 --> 01:23:20.041
